trans-unit.source: Represents a request to move focus to another control.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en begäran om att flytta fokus till en annan kontroll.

trans-unit.source: This class is used as an input parameter for the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen används som en indataparameter för den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A> method has a WPF framework-level override that provides a more practical implementation (<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), as well as a parallel implementation on <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> and <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A>metoden har en åsidosättning för WPF framework-nivå som ger en mer praktiska implementeringen (<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), samt en parallell implementering i <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement>och <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A>

trans-unit.source: You typically will set properties on TraversalRequest in order to customize the focusing behavior when you request that the focus be moved to another element.
trans-unit.target: Du kommer normalt ange egenskaper för TraversalRequest för att anpassa koncentrera beteende när du begär att fokus flyttas till ett annat element.

trans-unit.source: This class is also used as input parameters for the following methods: - <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, and implementations of that method that are used for interoperation (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen används också som indataparametrar för följande metoder:- <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, och implementeringar av metoden som används för interoperation (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The intended direction of the focus traversal, as a value of the enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Avsedda riktning fokus traversal, som ett värde för uppräkningen.

trans-unit.source: This property is read-only because the <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection> is a required input parameter of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest> class constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen är skrivskyddat eftersom det <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>är en obligatorisk indataparameter av den <xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest>klasskonstruktor.</xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>

trans-unit.source: One of the traversal direction enumeration values.
Gets or sets a value that indicates whether focus traversal has reached the end of child elements that can have focus.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om fokus traversal har nått slutet av underordnade element som kan ha fokus.

trans-unit.source: Focusable elements are those elements where the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A> property is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Tabbindexvärden element är dessa element där den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>egenskapen är `true`.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>

trans-unit.source: This parameter is primarily intended to communicate whether traversal using tab stops should wrap when calling the methods <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>,or.<xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den här parametern är främst avsett att kommunicera med tabbstopp traversal ska radbrytas vid anrop av metoderna <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>, eller.<xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you are passing focus to an object that implements <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>, then specifying true for Wrapped will result in that `true` value being passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Om du skickar fokus till ett objekt som implementerar <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>, sedan ange true för Wrapped leder som `true` värdet som skickas till den <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>implementering.</xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this traversal has reached the end of child elements that can have focus; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den här traversal har nått slutet av underordnade element som kan ha fokus; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
